## 6. FLUJO DE MODERACIÓN ADMIN

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant F as Frontend
    participant DB as Database
    participant A as Admin
    participant EF as Edge Function

    Note over U,A: CREACIÓN DE CONTENIDO
    U->>F: Crear Lote/Producto
    F->>DB: INSERT lotes/productos (status=pendiente)
    DB-->>F: Contenido creado
    F-->>U: "Tu publicación está en revisión"

    Note over U,A: NOTIFICACIÓN A ADMIN
    DB->>A: Dashboard muestra contenido pendiente

    Note over U,A: REVISIÓN ADMIN
    A->>F: Ver contenido pendiente
    F->>DB: SELECT * WHERE status=pendiente
    DB-->>F: Lista de contenido
    F-->>A: Mostrar items pendientes

    alt Aprobar Contenido
        A->>F: Click "Aprobar"
        F->>DB: UPDATE status=aprobado
        DB->>DB: INSERT auditoria_admin
        DB->>EF: notify-product-status / notify-status-change
        EF->>DB: INSERT notificaciones
        EF-->>U: "Tu publicación fue aprobada"
        DB-->>F: Actualizado
    else Rechazar Contenido
        A->>F: Click "Rechazar" + Notas
        F->>DB: UPDATE status=rechazado, admin_notes
        DB->>DB: INSERT auditoria_admin
        DB->>EF: notify-product-status / notify-status-change
        EF->>DB: INSERT notificaciones
        EF-->>U: "Tu publicación fue rechazada: [razón]"
    end

    Note over U,A: SUSPENDER USUARIO
    A->>F: Click "Suspender Usuario"
    F->>EF: Edge Function suspend-user
    EF->>DB: UPDATE profiles (is_active=false)
    EF->>DB: UPDATE auth.users (user_metadata.suspended=true)
    EF->>DB: INSERT notificaciones
    EF->>DB: INSERT auditoria_admin
    EF-->>U: "Tu cuenta ha sido suspendida"
    EF-->>A: "Usuario suspendido exitosamente"

    Note over U,A: RESTAURAR USUARIO
    A->>F: Click "Restaurar Usuario"
    F->>EF: Edge Function suspend-user (action=restore)
    EF->>DB: UPDATE profiles (is_active=true)
    EF->>DB: UPDATE auth.users (user_metadata.suspended=false)
    EF->>DB: INSERT notificaciones
    EF->>DB: INSERT auditoria_admin
    EF-->>U: "Tu cuenta ha sido restaurada"

    Note over U,A: ELIMINAR USUARIO PERMANENTEMENTE
    A->>F: Click "Eliminar Permanentemente"
    F->>EF: Edge Function delete-user-completely
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM ordenes WHERE user_id
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM calificaciones WHERE user_id
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM orden_mensajes WHERE user_id
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM notificaciones WHERE user_id
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM guias_guardadas WHERE user_id
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM lotes WHERE user_id
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM productos WHERE user_id
    EF->>DB: DELETE FROM profiles WHERE id
    EF->>DB: auth.admin.deleteUser(user_id)
    EF-->>A: "Usuario eliminado completamente"

    Note over U,A: GESTIÓN DE CALIFICACIONES REPORTADAS
    U->>F: Reportar calificación
    F->>DB: UPDATE calificaciones (reportada=true)
    DB-->>F: Calificación reportada
    
    A->>F: Ver calificaciones reportadas
    F->>DB: SELECT * WHERE reportada=true
    DB-->>F: Lista de reportes
    
    alt Ocultar Calificación
        A->>F: Click "Ocultar"
        F->>DB: UPDATE calificaciones (oculta=true)
    else Eliminar Calificación
        A->>F: Click "Eliminar"
        F->>DB: DELETE FROM calificaciones
    end
```

## 7. SISTEMA DE SEGURIDAD (RLS)

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Row-Level Security Policies"
        subgraph "profiles"
            P1[Users can view own profile]
            P2[Users can view active profiles]
            P3[Users can update own profile]
            P4[Admins can update any profile]
        end

        subgraph "lotes"
            L1[Users can view own lotes]
            L2[Users can view approved public lotes]
            L3[Admins can view all lotes]
            L4[Users can create own lotes]
            L5[Users can update own lotes]
            L6[Admins can update lote status]
        end

        subgraph "productos"
            PR1[Users can view approved available products]
            PR2[Users can view own products]
            PR3[Admins can view all products]
            PR4[Users can create own products]
            PR5[Admins can update product status]
        end

        subgraph "ordenes"
            O1[Users can view own orders as solicitante]
            O2[Users can view own orders as proveedor]
            O3[Admins can view all orders]
            O4[Users can create orders as solicitante]
            O5[Solicitante/Proveedor can update order]
        end

        subgraph "calificaciones"
            C1[Users can view relevant ratings]
            C2[Non-reported ratings are public]
            C3[Users can create ratings for completed orders]
            C4[Users can update own ratings]
            C5[Users can report ratings]
            C6[Admins can manage all ratings]
        end

        subgraph "notificaciones"
            N1[Users can view own notifications]
            N2[Users can update own notifications]
            N3[Users can delete own notifications]
        end

        subgraph "orden_mensajes"
            M1[Users can view messages from own orders]
            M2[Users can create messages in own orders]
            M3[Admins can manage all messages]
        end

        subgraph "auditoria_admin"
            A1[Only admins can access audit logs]
            A2[Users can insert audit logs for their actions]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Security Functions"
        SF1[is_current_user_admin]
        SF2[get_user_average_rating]
        SF3[get_user_rating_count]
        SF4[handle_new_user trigger]
        SF5[track_lote_status_change trigger]
        SF6[update_updated_at_column trigger]
    end
```

